data.description: Your new dream home awaits in Twin Lake Estates, Pride, LA. This 4-bedroom beauty was crafted in 2018 by Level Home Builders, boasting 2,200 sq. ft. of elegance with 12-foot ceilings. The spacious kitchen, complete with a gas stove, is perfect for entertaining, and there's even a dedicated office space for your work-life balance. But wait, there's more! Step outside to your private oasis – a backyard that'll make you swoon. Picture yourself in a heated pool and jacuzzi, all while sipping your favorite drink on the covered patio. The fenced-in yard overlooks a tranquil pond, creating the perfect backdrop for relaxation and unforgettable gatherings.  This desirable neighborhood is tucked away on a charming cul-de-sac, and convenient proximity to Southern University and Baton Rouge Metro Airport , making it the ideal place to call home. Don't miss out on this slice of paradise; it's waiting for you!
